<p>

Wolfram Burgard has received seven best paper awards from outstanding conferences. He also became a distinguished lecturer of the IEEE Robotics and Automation Society.</p>
<p>

In 2008, Wolfram Burgard became a fellow of the <social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
